		<h1 class="~text-3xl/5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What will you build?</h1>
		<div class="~text-base/lg ~mt-4/6 prose prose-muted dark:prose-invert text-pretty">
			<p>
				I'd love to see how you're using NumberFlow. Tag
				<Link href="https://x.com/mbarvian" target="_blank">@mbarvian</Link>
				in a post on X and I might include it here. Note: NumberFlow was previously called MotionNumber.
			</p>
		</div>
	</header>
